---
title: Mexican Fiesta Veggie Mince Enchiladas with Charred Corn Salsa & Cheddar Cheese
description: With veggie mince, tortillas, Cheddar cheese and salsa, this Mexican favourite is colourful, delicious and a heap of fun. Don’t
forget to dollop on the yoghurt to really get the fiesta going!
